    816  f3b9							;-------------------------------------------------------------
    817  f3b9							; CheckCollision - player vs the entity on the player's floor.
    818  f3b9							;   cone  -> +1 to the BCD score, entity consumed.
    819  f3b9							;   skull -> game over (freeze + red background).
    820  f3b9							;-------------------------------------------------------------
