   1170  f798							; DrawDigits - render the 48x8 score from Digit0..Digit5 pointers.
   1171  f798							; Page-aligned so BigLoop's branch stays in-page (exact 76-cycle rows).
   1172  f798							; After examples/6-digit-score.asm (Temp -> tempOne, LoopCount -> loopCnt).
